ent |publisher=Nydailynews.com |date= |accessdate=2011-09-30 |archive-date=2011-10-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111002142738/http://www.nydailynews.com/ny_local/2011/09/30/2011-09-30_russell_simmons_visits_occupy_wall_street_protesters_with_bottles_of_water_words.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>、[[Anti-Flag|Anti-Flag]]<ref>{{cite web |author= |url=http://www.anti-flag.com/?p=146 |title=Let's Occupy Wall Street! |publisher=anti-flag.com |date=2011-09-30 |accessdate=2011-10-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111009002746/http://www.anti-flag.com/?p=146 |archive-date=2011-10-09 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>、[[薩爾曼·魯西迪|薩爾曼·魯西迪]]、[[瑪格麗特·愛特伍|瑪格麗特·愛特伍]]、[[诺姆·乔姆斯基|诺姆·乔姆斯基]]和[[电台司令|电台司令]]<ref>{{cite web |author=Linda Solomon |url=http://www.vancouverobserver.com/politics/news/2011/09/30/michael-moore-susan-sarandon-margaret-atwood-and-noam-chomsky-throw-weight |title=Michael Moore, Susan Sarandon, Margaret Atwood and Noam Chomsky throw weight behind #OccupyWallSt protest |publisher=The Vancouver Observer |date= |accessdate=2011-09-30 |archive-date=2011-10-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111002163223/http://www.vancouverobserver.com/politics/news/2011/09/30/michael-moore-susan-sarandon-margaret-atwood-and-noam-chomsky-throw-weight |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

